reviewText: This is a pretty good concert.  Recorded in Europe,  He puts on a great live show with just him, a bass player and a drummer.  All the  songs are great.  Including a very rousing version of his signature song Polk Salad Annie.  And I always enjoy watching him play guitar and harmonica.

"Closer to the Truth" era TJW in Germany with a very strange audience. Thinking I may have seen this at a party a long time ago... not many pink Strats out there back then. Whether it was on TV or a tape I don't know but searched out the record after seeing the show. Glad to have found this.
